=======================================================================

Runtime-requirements:
 * Wt 3.1.10+: http://www.webtoolkit.eu/wt/doc/reference/html/InstallationUnix.html
   at least libwt, libwthttp, libwtsqlite3

Build-requirements:
 * g++ 4.5+ (lto is used in release version)
 * qmake
 * inkskape (Font Steve is used for logo and favicon)
 * convert by ImageMagick
 * upx (is used to compress release version)

To compile run `make`. The default target of make is building of debug
version of program. To build release version, run `make release`.

To run the program:
    make run-debug

